         APP_NAME=Your Agency
         APP_PRIMARY_COLOR=#0057B8
         APP_SECONDARY_COLOR=#003F84
         APP_TERTIARY_COLOR=#1A1A2E
    6. Add your own API keys:
         ONESIGNAL_APP_ID=...
         GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=...
